I found that SslStream in .NET Core 2.1/2.2/3.0 does not call BeginRead or ReadAsync of InnerStream when SslStream's BeginRead or ReadAsync are called.

Discussion at https://stackoverflow.com/questions/56431957/sslstream-does-not-call-beginread-or-readasync-of-innerstream-in-net-core-2-1 suggests this is because starting from .NET Core 2.1 the "core" APIs are no longer the byte-array ones; they'd be the Span ones.

